overview.en: The national medicine chain is a quality tracking service system for high-quality and truly healthy products. It is an innovative production and marketing channel for high-quality and truly healthy products. It is a dividend-based product for the profit distribution of blockchain health products. It is a strong application of virtual currency projects.
overview.zh: CMC100国医链是优质确真大健康产品的质量追踪服务体系，是优质确真大健康产品的创新生产和营销渠道，是区块链健康产品分销利润的分红币，是强应用的虚拟币项目。
